          20 Apr 2024 12:11 PM
          
          </div>
        <div class="ticker-item">4.To Prove S.27 Evidence Act Statement, Investigating Officer Must Narrate What Accused Stated; Merely Exhibiting Memorandum Not Enough : Supreme Court
